{"tid":1172008,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【我屌佢老母落地獄啦】私吞Marvel之父財產 Stan Lee生前遭虐待 前經理被捕或踎10年","createTime":"2019-05-26T06:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T10:56:03.000Z","uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc2236c9f225a073b30e349ef9f70f5fec0b31c","tid":1172008,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:37:22.000Z","msg":"Marvel之父史丹李（Stan Lee）於去年11月與世長辭，其生前拍檔Keya Morgan已在美國時間周六被警方拘捕，涉嫌曾虐待史丹李及侵吞財產。Keya Morgan是史丹李的好友兼經理人，史丹李在離世前已被指遭女兒Joan Celia Lee（J.C.）及Keya Morgan謀取財產、虐老兼代覆電郵，警方早在史丹李死前8個月開始針對Keya Morgan虐待老友嫌疑展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯警方公佈消息，Keya Morgan在10天前已被檢方以5項虐老罪名起訴，令曾非法禁錮史丹李及令受害人帶來身體傷害，用其財產進構成貪污、偽造、詐騙及偷竊，其中4項罪名為重罪，Keya Morgan如罪成最高可面臨入獄10年。<br />\n<br />\n據知，史丹李的財產總額達5,000萬美元（約3.9億），Keya Morgan被指疑挪用及私吞史丹李的財產達500萬美元（約3,900萬港元）。Keya Morgan將被送往洛杉磯受審，目前准以30萬美（約234萬港元）保釋。"},{"pid":"a03efa44afdbf3b412ea4975454cc317298b63d8","tid":1172008,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nyppagesix.files.wordpress.com/2019/05/stan-lee-keya-morgan-1.jpg?quality=90&amp;strip=all\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnyppagesix.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F05%2Fstan-lee-keya-morgan-1.jpg%3Fquality%3D90%26strip%3Dall&h=6d519a19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7816b623c0fa10a6931281e812ba8190863a2e7","tid":1172008,"uid":227275,"like":3,"dislike":31,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/EqfTtTr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqfTtTr.gif&h=0b61666f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cd6c92f4d137a77f2507ae5913f4078b1cc6855","tid":1172008,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"警方早在史丹李死前8個月開始針對Keya Morgan虐待<span style=\"color: red;\">老友</span>嫌疑展開調查<br />\n虐老定虐老友"},{"pid":"ab018476cbab00d2bf904b37